x_n \rightarrow a
c \in \mathbb{R}
cx_n \rightarrow ca
x_n \to a
n\to \infty
c\neq 0
\epsilon>0
n_0
n\geq n_0
\lvert cx_n - ca\rvert < \epsilon
\epsilon >0
x_n \to a
n \to \infty
n_0
